data.description: Welcome to your dream home in a prime location! This open concept modern luxury 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhome offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience. Nestled in a desirable neighborhood, this property is nearby shopping, dining, and all the amenities you desire. The sleek, modern kitchen boasts top-of-the-line appliances, ample storage, and a spacious island. It's a chef's paradise, perfect for preparing meals! The upper level features three generously-sized bedrooms, providing ample space and additional storage. The master suite includes a private ensuite bathroom. Enjoy the cooling AC, low maintenance and community perks. Schedule a viewing today and experience the lifestyle you've been dreaming of!
